{
    "name": "Young Magma Dragon",
    "type": "monster",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Temperamental and prone to violent outbursts, magma dragons are regarded by most other dragons as dangerously insane\u2014an assumption that, more often than not, proves correct. One can rarely predict a magma dragon\u2019s state of mind until it either attacks or attempts to engage in conversation. For their part, magma dragons can justify all of their actions\u2014they just rarely feel the need to do so."
        }
    ],
    "html": "<i>Between this dragon\u2019s jet-black scales run glowing rivulets of lava, and veins aglow with heat shine in the membranes of its wings. </i>",
